---
title: Caribbean Lentil, Beef & Veggie Pie with Coconut Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing beef and lentil pie! A coconutty,
Caribbean-spiced lentil filling meets a golden potato topping for a dish that's equally wholesome and delish.
